パッケージ jp.innovationplus.ipp.client

クラスの概要
IPPApplicationResourceClient IPPPublicResourceClient : REST Client for ApplicationResource
IPPApplicationResourceClient.QueryCondition QueryCondition : Helper class for building the search criteria for ApplicationResource
IPPGeoLocationClient IPPGeoLocationClient : REST Client for GeoLocation
IPPGeoLocationClient.QueryCondition QueryCondition : Helper class for building the search criteria for GeoLocation
IPPGeoResourceClient IPPGeoResourceClient : REST Client for GeoResource
IPPGeoResourceClient.QueryCondition QueryCondition : Helper class for building the search criteria for GeoResource
IPPLoginClient IPPLoginClient : Login Client
IPPProfileClient IPPProfileClient : REST Client for Profile
IPPProfileClient.Fields Fields : Helper class for building the needed fields for Profile
